  "detailed_description": "The game is fully compatible with Steam Deck.<br><br>Step into a combat-free Metroidvania world where your adventure revolves around exploration, puzzle-solving, and treasure hunt. <br><br>Feature<br>- Multiplayer mode (2-4 players) to coop or race with your friends<br>- Easy to learn, hard to master<br>- Story with mystery <br>- No combat <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276600/extras/3e6141d09967404da4726b4caf90f7fc.poster.avif?t=1741569727\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276600/extras/3e6141d09967404da4726b4caf90f7fc.webm?t=1741569727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276600/extras/3e6141d09967404da4726b4caf90f7fc.mp4?t=1741569727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Time to 100%: 4 hours <br><br>Being a WELL-like game, we provide: <br>- Solving the platform puzzle with player creativity, more than 1 solution in most places<br>- Unlock abilities in different sequence can provide difference gameplay and experience <br>- accumulated knowledge allows more efficient speedrunnings  <br>- Bonus content to reward player who clear the game within a period of game<br>- Animals (just kidding)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276600/extras/91a8c893afa2f5f54a3f7de93ac32edf.poster.avif?t=1741569727\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276600/extras/91a8c893afa2f5f54a3f7de93ac32edf.webm?t=1741569727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276600/extras/91a8c893afa2f5f54a3f7de93ac32edf.mp4?t=1741569727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>But to be honest, we don't have:<br>- Puzzle that strongly require a hardcore gamer community<br>- Boss fight<br>- Gorgeous particle effects<br>- Ultra-small capacity<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276600/extras/84a4b192220ded9f9695794fabb44b97.poster.avif?t=1741569727\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276600/extras/84a4b192220ded9f9695794fabb44b97.webm?t=1741569727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276600/extras/84a4b192220ded9f9695794fabb44b97.mp4?t=1741569727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>If you like this game, please play Animal-WELL.",
  "about_the_game": "The game is fully compatible with Steam Deck.<br><br>Step into a combat-free Metroidvania world where your adventure revolves around exploration, puzzle-solving, and treasure hunt. <br><br>Feature<br>- Multiplayer mode (2-4 players) to coop or race with your friends<br>- Easy to learn, hard to master<br>- Story with mystery <br>- No combat <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276600/extras/3e6141d09967404da4726b4caf90f7fc.poster.avif?t=1741569727\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276600/extras/3e6141d09967404da4726b4caf90f7fc.webm?t=1741569727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276600/extras/3e6141d09967404da4726b4caf90f7fc.mp4?t=1741569727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Time to 100%: 4 hours <br><br>Being a WELL-like game, we provide: <br>- Solving the platform puzzle with player creativity, more than 1 solution in most places<br>- Unlock abilities in different sequence can provide difference gameplay and experience <br>- accumulated knowledge allows more efficient speedrunnings  <br>- Bonus content to reward player who clear the game within a period of game<br>- Animals (just kidding)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276600/extras/91a8c893afa2f5f54a3f7de93ac32edf.poster.avif?t=1741569727\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276600/extras/91a8c893afa2f5f54a3f7de93ac32edf.webm?t=1741569727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276600/extras/91a8c893afa2f5f54a3f7de93ac32edf.mp4?t=1741569727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>But to be honest, we don't have:<br>- Puzzle that strongly require a hardcore gamer community<br>- Boss fight<br>- Gorgeous particle effects<br>- Ultra-small capacity<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276600/extras/84a4b192220ded9f9695794fabb44b97.poster.avif?t=1741569727\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276600/extras/84a4b192220ded9f9695794fabb44b97.webm?t=1741569727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276600/extras/84a4b192220ded9f9695794fabb44b97.mp4?t=1741569727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>If you like this game, please play Animal-WELL.",
